{"tid":176940,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"油頭油臉毒撚脫暗倉日記","createTime":"2017-03-28T13:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T15:57:43.000Z","uid":28318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f94c78ae8dad9a5bdbf96f946ec52a9d2499ef23","tid":176940,"uid":28318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T13:36:40.000Z","msg":"由細到大都係暗倉底<br />\n做過針清 - 其實係幾好，因為幫我做個個姨姨係熟人，次次淨針清都搞成個鐘，逐個毛孔搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee4c70ec1d530ea0e5ab5d96c85c0ca11f30498","tid":176940,"uid":3130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T13:37:41.000Z","msg":"油頭油臉毒撚留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e133107c232702a7292411e77ccec181cd32fd56","tid":176940,"uid":28318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T13:38:04.000Z","msg":"之後嫌麻煩停咗做<br />\nkeep住爆下倉又停下"},{"pid":"26cfe2bbb8a19fed07d5fb1d42614d7b44459ac4","tid":176940,"uid":72342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T13:39:19.000Z","msg":"樓主  我都係油面   油頭   不過用左天然方法呢加好左勁多"},{"pid":"ea5213f6a3f1c060f19ae3066b4480da288bb3fe","tid":176940,"uid":8317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T13:39:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由細到大都係暗倉底<br />\n做過針清 - 其實係幾好，因為幫我做個個姨姨係熟人，次次淨針清都搞成個鐘，逐個毛孔搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我塊面都係好差，原來真係會有 facial 幫人逐個逐個毛孔咁清 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會好貴？好想整下"},{"pid":"7d5ea6241c66dc9be8ac66b071810d7e4943cd9f","tid":176940,"uid":33567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T13:41:31.000Z","msg":"冇膿嘅石頭瘡點搞 成半年都唔退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e47afe37702858407a9922baa805e779d97a4a","tid":176940,"uid":28318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T13:42:55.000Z","msg":"直到去外國個時唔知係咪去旅行時太懶，爆到爛臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔係紅都腫起個啲，但都睇到成臉係<br />\n<br />\n之後grad左返香港又慢慢好啲無咩新倉出<br />\n<br />\n直到半年前轉咗份西工<br />\n人生第一次爆壓力倉 (我估)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/a/1cyRu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2F1cyRu&h=b17501c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3907db6167e036126151bd185f7b7280142add0","tid":176940,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T13:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01095d294d29c3a4c9e33cf59833b43fb0d17d6","tid":176940,"uid":34352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T13:45:54.000Z","msg":"去過針清，搞到毛孔大哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然係有好左，但d毛孔勁粗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9eaa6d3fd0a7b88c976c6953c49df0ad71750c","tid":176940,"uid":74315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T13:46:41.000Z","msg":"屌 如果你真係好油 又成面粒粒暗瘡<br />\n針清係治標唔治本<br />\n食a酸啦<br />\n利申：油底暗瘡皮膚 十年抗戰經驗 咩都試過 而家食緊a酸"},{"pid":"8a9861a28f559d999e49448d799caa3b82f824bf","tid":176940,"uid":28318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T13:49:02.000Z","msg":"正題，前日呀媽話揾檻欖油漱口可以消毒，用完仲好清爽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就上網睇下<br />\n點知原來好多人都用檻欖油洗臉<br />\n我岩岩試完<br />\n真係幾正 <img src=\"http://imgur.com/a/5kivw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2F5kivw&h=9b4e0288&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n會日日keep住update睇下係咪真係少啲粒粒同去印"},{"pid":"3324615f7342275972276ad1fc321f6db54d2c0b","tid":176940,"uid":28318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T13:50:58.000Z","msg":"其實琴晚有試過用髮油大島樁油洗臉<br />\n洗完之後雖然係少咗粒粒<br />\n但臉2邊甩哂皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb44baf6d77f66d5a98090343956b0e9e83e855","tid":176940,"uid":75704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T13:51:00.000Z","msg":"成塊面都係印 留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4bf80e707dffa8389d3bd15b2a1304e2205a08","tid":176940,"uid":28318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T13:53:47.000Z","msg":"啲圖係咪load唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://holland.pk/hoc70a3n\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhoc70a3n&h=8248f6b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今晚第一次用檻欖油洗臉<br />\n加左鹽做磨沙<br />\n塊臉好滑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但未甩哂皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468a1fbfc0635de75570a801c1300f3715c40bb1","tid":176940,"uid":28318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T13:54:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主  我都係油面   油頭   不過用左天然方法呢加好左勁多</blockquote><br />\n咩方法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想快d去印"},{"pid":"d991c9b7123d316e08faaa990c90ff3154322fa4","tid":176940,"uid":28318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T13:55:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>由細到大都係暗倉底<br />\n做過針清 - 其實係幾好，因為幫我做個個姨姨係熟人，次次淨針清都搞成個鐘，逐個毛孔搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我塊面都係好差，原來真係會有 facial 幫人逐個逐個毛孔咁清 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會好貴？好想整下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個auntie係幫開貴婦做，係太子，我估唔平"},{"pid":"bd62588948bdc727489879904c644e295b1ee6bb","tid":176940,"uid":28318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T13:55:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇膿嘅石頭瘡點搞 成半年都唔退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會痛到死都係咁jit佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d94059be0bff6716c1306d12fb601d84f14c99","tid":176940,"uid":28318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T13:56:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 如果你真係好油 又成面粒粒暗瘡<br />\n針清係治標唔治本<br />\n食a酸啦<br />\n利申：油底暗瘡皮膚 十年抗戰經驗 咩都試過 而家食緊a酸</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔敢食，成日聽人講有副作用又會返發 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37273a7f26fc7d7dffff13c8203c9a5c9e1716f","tid":176940,"uid":33567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T13:59:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇膿嘅石頭瘡點搞 成半年都唔退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會痛到死都係咁jit佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個有凹洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3b74649f70a3a10ec687786b7d5cf303f18a39","tid":176940,"uid":28318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:03:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冇膿嘅石頭瘡點搞 成半年都唔退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會痛到死都係咁jit佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個有凹洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我都係成臉疤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f15dbb76adcf642695d5abd3f0ccbfd67de281","tid":176940,"uid":72342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:23:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主  我都係油面   油頭   不過用左天然方法呢加好左勁多</blockquote><br />\n咩方法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想快d去印</blockquote><br />\n我用 個 冰河泥   一星期fu 兩次面   呢加額頭冇曬印     但係塊面仲出緊瘡   呢加仲青春期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   有d位  無法避免"},{"pid":"597d7147d2691327bfa32202eed686bbf9a6666a","tid":176940,"uid":72342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:23:53.000Z","msg":"同埋我係食 勁清淡既人  以前讀書個陣  起勢食m記  油野食   呢加轉清"},{"pid":"1b2df65baa0cdd56b81d1764826cf5801a864d30","tid":176940,"uid":74315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:21:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌 如果你真係好油 又成面粒粒暗瘡<br />\n針清係治標唔治本<br />\n食a酸啦<br />\n利申：油底暗瘡皮膚 十年抗戰經驗 咩都試過 而家食緊a酸</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔敢食，成日聽人講有副作用又會返發 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跟體重計去食 8成人唔會番發 就算番發都唔會好似未食咁嚴重<br />\n趁未有凹凸洞之前早啲食啦<br />\n我俾左成5萬美容雞啦 大公司細公司都試過<br />\n次次都係做完一兩日滑 <br />\n不如俾兩萬食a酸一勞永逸"},{"pid":"776345fe8083bab6c5e7903a078fbc5f3c54a4db","tid":176940,"uid":28318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T15:56:57.000Z","msg":"Day2<br />\n<br />\n再用檻欖油洗臉<br />\n洗個時摔咗好多粒粒出來好爽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但之後再用洗臉泡洗個時2邊臉有啲乸乸地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後查cream都有啲乸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該無咩事掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6xtoec9u\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6xtoec9u&h=d21df2e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到塊臉咁真係好想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dee2c191528c8a89c63bb0441411b45cb26705a","tid":176940,"uid":28318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T15:57:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌 如果你真係好油 又成面粒粒暗瘡<br />\n針清係治標唔治本<br />\n食a酸啦<br />\n利申：油底暗瘡皮膚 十年抗戰經驗 咩都試過 而家食緊a酸</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔敢食，成日聽人講有副作用又會返發 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跟體重計去食 8成人唔會番發 就算番發都唔會好似未食咁嚴重<br />\n趁未有凹凸洞之前早啲食啦<br />\n我俾左成5萬美容雞啦 大公司細公司都試過<br />\n次次都係做完一兩日滑 <br />\n不如俾兩萬食a酸一勞永逸</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已經成臉都係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}